data-triple-N3.o: "The New Democratic Party (NDP) (French: Nouveau Parti democratique, NPD) is a social democratic federal political party in Canada. The current leader of the NDP is Thomas Mulcair, who was elected in the 2012 leadership election. The NDP was founded in 1961 out of the merger of the Co-operative Commonwealth Federation (CCF) with the Canadian Labour Congress (CLC). The provincial wings of the NDP in Manitoba and Nova Scotia currently form the governments in those provinces."@en
